        "answer": "(1) E[L] = 0.04×120,000 = NT$4,800 per year. (2) If premium grossly exceeds expected loss plus risk tolerance and deductible friction, retention may dominate; if bankruptcy risk from one loss, transfer may dominate. (3) GPS locks, secured storage, marked gear. / (1) 4,800 元。(2) 若完全自留期望成本低於保費加自負額摩擦且能承受單次全損，可傾向自留；反之移轉。(3) 例如保險櫃、機身刻字、固定存放。",
